"Every Heartbeat Matters Impacts More Than One Million Underserved Patients Ahead of 2020 Goal, including Fatma of Sudan Now 14, Fatma was nine-years-old when she stopped going to school in West Kordofan, Sudan due to recurring headaches, weight loss and general discomfort.",EW_2018.pdf
"Initially, her mother and father turned to the city hospital for help.",EW_2018.pdf
They were advised to search for a more accurate diagnosis in the capital city of Khartoum.,EW_2018.pdf
