"Edwards Lifesciences 2020 EHS Report 36 At our Dominican Republic manufacturing plant, our wastewater treatment plant not only treats domestic and industry wastewater before discharge to the POTW, but also allows us to recycle and return 25% of the treated wastewater to our non‐ potable water sources for reuse, such as toilets and chillers , thereby reducing our total water discharge volume.",EW_2020.pdf
