Agency representatives approved all of our preventive and response measures and issued no findings or recommendations at any of our sites.,EW_2020.pdf
"Third Party Audits: Due to restrictions on travel and in order to meet our protocols to help prevent the spread of COVID -19, on- site 3 rd Party audits were not conducted at our manufacturing sites in 2020.",EW_2020.pdf
"However, we are in the process to implement these audits later in 2021 after COVID -19 vaccinations are administered and travel and quarantine restrictions are lifted.",EW_2020.pdf
