"Globally, Edwards underwent 23 government agency inspections, which resulted in no concerns or notices of violation.",EW_2020.pdf
"In 2020, we had 10 separate health agency inspections and inquiries with regards to maintaining our COVID -19 protocols and meeting local government health agency requirements.",EW_2020.pdf
Agency representatives approved all of our preventive and response measures and issued no findings or significant recommendations at any of our sites.,EW_2020.pdf
"Voluntary Environmental Agreements Since 1995, Edwards has partnered with the California Regional Water Quality Control Board (RWQCB) to address the remediation of contaminated groundwater at a former manufacturing location in Irvine, California.",EW_2020.pdf
Remediation activities are aimed at cleaning up low levels of freon detected in the groundwater.,EW_2020.pdf
