"In addition, in 2020 there were no offsite spills or releases to ground, air or water.",EW_2020.pdf
The environmental impacts of our operations meet regulator y requirements and industry best practices for pollution prevention.,EW_2020.pdf
Our EHS impacts are reported in other relevant sections of this Report.,EW_2020.pdf
