HIGHLIGHT STORIES 61 EDWARDS LIFESCIENCES 2021 SUSTAINABILITY REPORT Volunteerism & Giving Edwards Lifesciences’ work to encourage employee charitable activity and giving supports our culture and aspiration of passionate engagement that strengthens our communities.,EW_2021.pdf
"Definition Dedicating time, talent and resources to communities where Edwards’ employees live and work and supporting community health and well-being.",EW_2021.pdf
"Our charitable activities and giving efforts focus on impacting underserved structural heart and critically ill patients through our Every Heartbeat Matters initiative which increases access to healthcare via humanitarian care, as well as strengthens the communities where we live and work.",EW_2021.pdf
